'''Baker-Ollis合成'''（Baker-Ollis synthesis）

邻[[羟基|羟基]][[芳基|芳基]]芳甲基甲酮与[[乙氧基|乙氧基]][[草酰氯|草酰氯]]在[[吡啶|吡啶]]存在下进行反应，发生[[缩合|缩合]][[环化|环化]]作用，产物再经[[水解|水解]]、[[脱羧|脱羧]]，可得[[异黄酮|异黄酮]][[衍生物|衍生物]]。<ref>{{cite journal en|title=A New Synthesis of isoFlavones|author=Baker W., Ollis W. D.|journal=[[Nature_(journal)|Nature]]|volume=169|issue=4304|pages=706|year=1952|doi=10.1038/169706a0}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal en|title=A new synthesis of isoflavones. Part I|author=Wilson Baker, J. Chadderton, J. B. Harborne and W. D. Ollis|journal=[[J._Chem._Soc.|J. Chem. Soc.]]|year=1953|pages=1852–1860|doi=10.1039/JR9530001852}}</ref><ref>Warburton W. K., ''Quart. Rev.'', '''1954''', 8, 79. </ref>

